{"article_id":"tpYepb9kZ4FldJRV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump lashed out at Congress Thursday ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"blasting lawmakers","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"for failing to fund his border wall demands","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and increasing the likelihood of a partial government shutdown later in the week .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"House Speaker Paul D. Ryan said","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"the president informed lawmakers at a White House meeting","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that he will not sign a stopgap spending bill","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"the Senate passed Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that would keep the government running through Feb. 8 .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Ryan said","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"the president has \" legitimate concerns \" about border security .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"\" So what we ' re going to do is go back to the House","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"and work with our members , \"","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Ryan said .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" We want to keep the government open ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"but we also want to see an agreement","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that protects the border . \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Lawmakers have to pass new spending legislation before a midnight Friday deadline","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"or risk a partial shutdown of government operations .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"House Republicans were prepping legislation later Thursday","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"that would extend through Feb. 8 money for federal departments","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"that aren ' t already funded for the full year .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The House version would also provide an additional $ 5.7 billion in 2019 for U.S. Customs and Border Protection \" procurement , construction , and improvements \" and additional money for disaster relief .","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"The Dow Jones Industrial average slumped nearly 500 points Thursday amid the uncertain signals out of Washington .","depth":2},{"id":24,"text":"At a White House event Thursday afternoon , Mr. Trump said","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"he planned to stay strong in the fight .","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"Earlier in the day , Mr. Trump suggested","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"he was betrayed by \" leadership \" on Capitol Hill","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"who had promised","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"after another spending bill earlier this year","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"he would get border security money .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"\" It didn ' t happen !","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"We foolishly fight for border security for other countries","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"- but not for our beloved U.S.A.","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Not good ! \"","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"the president said via Twitter .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Before Mr. Trump met with House lawmakers ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"the White House had followed up with a statement","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"the president was not inclined to sign the stopgap spending bill","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"without money for border barriers .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"\" The president is continuing to weigh his options , \"","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders said .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Trump , in his tweet , didn ' t say","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"which party ' s \" leadership \"","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"he felt","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"betrayed him ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"but the GOP has been in control of Congress for the past two years ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and has struggled to deliver on his demands for cash for a wall .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Earlier this week , the White House said","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"it could sign a spending bill","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"without additional money for the border fence","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"because it was going to scrounge the cash from other agencies ' budgets .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"But after fierce criticism from conservative commentators and lawmakers on Capitol Hill , the president appears to have changed that stance .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The spending bill passed the Senate by voice vote late Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"suggesting","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"there are eager to avoid a shutdown showdown .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"But House conservatives are more eager to foment a blowup .","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"House Republicans met Thursday morning","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"but didn ' t appear to reach any conclusions .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"\" We had a really good meeting and candid conversation with our members .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"There ' s a strong desire","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to find a way","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to get the president the money","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"he needs ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"the tools","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"he needs ,","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"to secure our border","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"and build a wall , \"","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"said House Majority Whip Steve Scalise .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Mr. Scalise said","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"there are also discussions","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"going on","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"about disaster relief funding ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"which some lawmakers want to add to the spending bill .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi told reporters","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that she ' d have to see what the offer would be on disaster assistance -","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"but that her members will not support additional money for a U.S.-Mexico border wall .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"\" We ' re right in the middle of a sort of a meltdown on the part of the Republicans , \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Mr. Ryan had spoken with Mr. Trump by phone before the White House meeting .","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"Members","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"exiting a meeting of House Republicans","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"gave conflicting messages","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"on whether they had gotten assurances","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"that Mr. Trump would sign the short-term bill .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" There ' s no question","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"this would be signed , \"","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"said Rep. Chris Collins , New York Republican .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"Other members said","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"they were awaiting clearer signals from the president .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"\" There is definitely uncertainty about the president ' s position","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"on finding funding for a border wall , \"","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"said Rep. Mo Brooks , Alabama Republican .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":189,"left":118,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":117,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":113,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":98,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":0,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":96,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":110,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":102,"right":109,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":4,"right":101,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":5,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"l